        <abstract> 
<p>Finds no absolute differences in size of sexes of <hi rend="italic">Copridae</hi>. Gives several other genera in which males are larger than females.</p>  
<p>Confirms his view of stridulation organ of house cricket. [see <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> 1: 354–5.]</p> 
            <p>Tells CD of a powerful convert to Darwinism: H. von Kiesenwetter of Berlin.</p>
        </abstract>
